, paratype, Namibia, Naukluft, aedeagus; D) 
<taxonomicName id="4C2E81F1F713CA74B8BAF866C76F7FE7" authority="Bilton, 2022" authorityName="Bilton" authorityYear="2022" box="[1009,1082,1967,1991]" class="Insecta" family="Hydraenidae" genus="Protozantaena" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="94" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="birdi" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="B95A2660F713CA74B8BAF866C76F7FE7" box="[1009,1082,1967,1991]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="94">P. birdi</emphasis>
